Name: Lost Summoner Kitty
About the game: Monsters appearing one after another. Let's summon a companion who is reliable and get rid of and defeat the enemies by the number of quotas by the time limit. But the enemies are fighting counterattacks, if they are not guarded they will be full of monsters and they will not be able to win. Use the characteristics of your friends and aim for game clear! ! Monsters do not have money. But if you break the crystal that appears on the stage you will be money! Earn bonus by clearing the stage earlier! You can strengthen your friends by using money. All 20 stages without save. Simple play! Features of this game Casual Strategy game easy to play with simple operation Attack character, collection character, personality character with improved ability Growth factors that can enhance character All 20 stages, unexpected volume
